Vibe Graphing Intent: SaaS Shadow Pro (Problem-Led Solutions)

Model Configuration:
- Build Model (Architect): Gemini 2.0 Flash
- Invoke Model (Worker): opencode:ollama

Design Intent:
Construct an autonomous system for the SaaS Shadow Entrepreneur arm of the business. 
The focus is on identifying high-impact business "pain points" (e.g., HMRC processes, administrative friction) 
and delivering professional "Engagement Prospectives" that include detailed plans, costs, instructions, and legal documentation. 
The system must test the real-world ability to build solutions while qualifying engagement.

Structural Constraints (Topology):
START -> [Pain_Miner] -> [Solution_Architect] -> [Prospective_Author] -> [Engagement_Qualifier] -> END

Pain_Miner: Scans beyond Reddit to reputable platforms (LinkedIn, Upwork, Govt Portals) for procedural pain points.
Solution_Architect: Designs and tests modular SaaS or automated solutions (e.g., SlipStream HMRC Automator).
Prospective_Author: Generates branded engagement packages (HTML/PDF) containing Plans, Costs, Instructions, and Legal docs.
Engagement_Qualifier: Monitors client interactions via email and qualificies leads based on data-driven intent.

Data Contracts:
- PULL: .mira/scores/saas_pro_fidelity.json, industry compliance docs, previous Antigravity session logs.
- PUSH: .brain/outputs/saas_pro_workspaces/client_report.html, .mira/scores/engagement_qualification.json.

Context Adapters:
- PathRAG: Access "SlipStream" audit logic and historical "Battle-Testing" logs from HMRC-related tasks.
- MCP: Utilize 'saas-shadow-pro' skill and 'client-delivery' for professional handoffs.

Role Assignment:
- Miner: 🔬 Scientific Method + ⚛️ First Principles
- Architect: ✨ Creative Synthesis + ⚙️ Pragmatic Application
- Author: ✨ Creative Synthesis + 🤔 Philosophical Inquiry
- Qualifier: ⚙️ Pragmatic Application + 🌑 The Dark Passenger
